overview.en: Ubiquitous Social Network Service (USNS) token is designed and used as an exclusive incentive token platform to inspire and encourage individuals who can share their redundant computing and bandwidth resources as caching or relay nodes for YouTube views. This also motivates creators and viewers of YouTube videos in online economic activity. It's only a matter of time before every retailer is using blockchain in some capacity. More importantly, USNS allows worldwide YouTube viewers to engage each other, drive revenues, and shopping experience on the USNS platform.
